&= (1 \cdot 5.004 - 1 \cdot 1.677)\hat{I} + (1 \cdot 1 - 1 \cdot 5.004)\hat{J} + (1 \cdot 1.677 - 1 \cdot 1)\hat{K} \\
&= 3.327\hat{I} - 4.004\hat{J} + 1.677\hat{K}
\end{align*}
\]

Now, we can calculate the magnitude of the cross product using the formula:

\[
